preference.name: SS1_DASS_shape_default
preference.preference_description: Defines the shape similarity used by the Shape Search solution in the Active Workspace client. Please contact the Shape Search administrator to confirm the available shape similarity configurations. Assuming that the shape similarities defined by the administrator as a gradient from identical to similar, the valid values would be 0 to 9 with 0 being the most identical.
